    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "The War Department has furnished this Bureau with the following",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "telegram dated July 5 at New York, New York:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "\"FOR FURTHER DETAILS CONCERNING FLYING DISKS SUGGEST",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "IMMEDIATE CONTACT OF [REDACTED] 66",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "ILLINOIS WHO MAY HAVE IMPORTANT INFORMATION CONCERN-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "ING THEIR ORIGIN.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "The War Department has furnished a memorandum entitled \"Report on",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Flying Saucers\", dated July 7, 1947, addressed to Commanding General, 32d AAF",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "Base Unit, Bolling Field, Washington D. C., from John D. Schindler, Jr., two",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "copies of which are attached. The War Department has stated that the incidents 66",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "referred to in the attached memorandum are in the general vicinity of [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "which was given as the address of [REDACTED] in the above telegram.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "It is, therefore, desired that the Chicago Field Division conduct",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "appropriate inquiries regarding [REDACTED] and in the event such inquiries do 66",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "not reveal information indicating that he should not be interviewed, he",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "should be interrogated for any information he might have relative to flying",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "discs. It is desired that this matter be handled as soon as possible and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
